    <h1>Lokmangal Setu - Child Safety Standards</h1>
    
    <h2>Our Commitment to Child Safety</h2>
    <p>Lokmangal Setu is committed to providing a safe environment for all users and has zero tolerance for child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) and child sexual abuse material (CSAM).</p>
    
    <h2>Prevention Measures</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Proactive content moderation and monitoring</li>
        <li>User reporting mechanisms for inappropriate content</li>
        <li>Age verification processes where applicable</li>
        <li>Regular safety audits and updates</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Reporting Mechanism</h2>
    <p>Users can report child safety concerns directly within the app. All reports are reviewed immediately and appropriate action is taken.</p>
    
    <h2>Legal Compliance</h2>
    <p>We comply with all relevant child safety laws and report violations to appropriate regional and national authorities as required.</p>
    
    <h2>Response Actions</h2>
    <p>Violations result in immediate account suspension, content removal, and reporting to law enforcement when required.</p>
    
